kwNRGDbO7jg-8czNOJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCA33kwNRGDbO7jg-8czNOJQ&d=UZACy8ioDmpAs2uy0tT7%2Bf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=39b4cf4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCA33kwNRGDbO7jg-8czNOJQ</a><br />\n依家都慢慢多人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇得出用心拍 會拍觀眾想睇既餐廳<br />\n係唔係廣告都講得一清二楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲食評都算有內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n都有些少旅遊vlog 剪接得幾好仲有自己上字幕<br />\n<br />\n第二個係使徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Jo_W-PsLjjOBin5vVC2Vw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC9Jo_W-PsLjjOBin5vVC2Vw&d=UZACy8ioDmpAs2uy0tT7%2Bf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3e8f203d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Jo_W-PsLjjOBin5vVC2Vw</a><br />\n我覺得唔應該用高質形容 因為佢拍片器材好簡陋 只係佢部電話同一支mic<br />\n應該係用清泉黎形容 UP片快<br />\nAlfred試放題多 使徒就試好多小店/新假期好鍾意推介既過江龍餐廳 見佢都成日踩唔少伏<br />\n係唔係廣告都會講得好清楚<br />\n但冇記錯佢咁耐以黎好似都冇餐廳搵佢做廣告 得啲牌子寄野俾佢試食<br />\n閒時唔知食咩可以上佢channel望望 起碼可信過openrice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a184cd3b53cd8fdaf84ab32ca78b05257a175fa4","tid":749351,"uid":71543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d67b8c459c6189b630a2cea95b69b405e0a79c7e","tid":749351,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"757e88699bc98de000084e192d4165509aaab0dc","tid":749351,"uid":71543,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"我發現大家都唔知咩叫冇人識<br />\n百幾萬subscirber都拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:49:51.000Z","msg":"咁要睇你定義「少人」係指少香港人睇定少全世界人睇，<br />\n上面講少香港人睇pewdiepie我又覺得合理喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"多人識但少人睇<br />\npewdiepie係食唔中香港市場 其實外國youtuber都好難係香